    <title>Hexo安装资源压缩插件报错，Command failed: C:&#92;Windows&#92;system32&#92;cmd.exe /s /c &quot;autoreconf -ivf&quot;</title>
    <url>/2023/06/07/%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="解决方案"><a href="#解决方案" class="headerlink" title="解决方案"></a>解决方案</h1><div class="note-large blue"><div class="notel-title"><p>修改windows的hosts文件</p>
</div><div class="notel-content"><p>修改C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts<br>添加一行<br>151.101.76.133    raw.githubusercontent.com</p>
</div></div>
<p>然后就可以愉快安装了</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Shell"><figure class="iseeu highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-all-minifier --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>]]></content>
